reviews.reviewText: I just recently have been able to use these packing cubes, and I must say that I love these cubes more because have a handle. It makes taking them in and out of my duffle bag real easy, and handling them once taken out tof the suitcase. Being that this set has 4 cubes, you can pack a lot of things for one trip.I used mine for an overnight trip and was able to store all of my clothing items in one cube with some room to spare. I am looking forward to using these cubes on my next family vacation. I also got the medium cubes, for the sake of comparing space. Being that I had some room left in the large cube, I am going to try the medium cube for my one night excursions.From the looks of the bag, it is durable, but you never know until you get a chance to really try them out. I gave it 4 stars based on my examination of the product and the minimal use I have had so far.
